14 accredited colleges or universities presenting evidence of
15 the completion of course work and clinical practicum
16 requirements equivalent to that required by the Council on
17 Academic Accreditation of the American Speech-Language-
18 Hearing Association or other accrediting agency approved by
19 the board;
20 (3) Present written evidence of completion of a
21 clinical fellowship from supervisors. The experience
22 required by this subdivision shall follow the completion of
23 the requirements of subdivisions (1) and (2) of this
24 section. This period of employment shall be under the
25 direct supervision of a [person who is licensed by the state
